
Node:	wave_greeting (Speech response to waving gesture)
Input:
	struct xz[]
Config: 
	x.proximity: 
		center: 120
		max to the right: 240
		max to the left: 0
	Gesture wave:
		z.proximity is within 5% of all z.proximity in xz
		x.proximity begins rising and then starts falling, then rises and falls again
Output:
	None
Steps:
	1. Initialization: Begin subscribing to tpc_gesture (100Hz)
	2. if wave is detected, then
		(a) send request to srv_speaker ("Hello")